You can use the asterisk wildcard to represent all values as follows:
[*] Represents all values of an array index. For example, the wildcards in the following field path allow you to mask the social security number of every employee in every division in the company:Division[*]/Employee[*]/SSN
/* Represents all values for an element of a map. For example, Division[*]/Employee[*]is element the right word?
